      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_8173646945690832148.png",
                "id": "talent72099",
                "key": "Strike of the Dispossessed ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Strike of the Dispossessed "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, draw 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Awaken, My Kindred</span> card and create 1 stack of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oasis Nourishment</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Oasis Nourishment</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you play Awaken, My Kindred:</span> Spend 1 less Elemental Die.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">U</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">sage(s): 1</span> (Up to 3 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/b5c63ab0dca603b7744290cd57df7ba6_7444997897286566553.png",
                "id": "talent8873",
                "key": "Life Stream",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Life Stream"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, draw 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Awaken, My Kindred</span> card and create 2 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oasis Nourishment</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Oasis Nourishment</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you play Awaken, My Kindred:</span> Spend 1 less Elemental Die.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Up to 3 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/7abf617a4cbf7dfd0d8af8ea344109a0_6347005362530748689.png",
                "id": "talent53483",
                "key": "The End Falls",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The End Falls"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When battle begins, create 6 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Awaken, My Kindred</span> and place them randomly into your deck. After you summon 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Proliferated Organism</span>, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Reignited Heart of Oasis</span> and obtains 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield</span> points.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Reignited Heart of Oasis</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br>The character to which this is attached deals +3 DMG.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character to which this is attached uses a Skill:</span> Remove the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oasis Nourishment</span> on your side. Each stack removed heals the attached character for 1 HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/78668ff054322fa748bbe935edb4a58e_909119730618315669.png",
                "id": "talent68241",
                "key": "Invokation of Propagation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Invokation of Propagation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Event Card</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you play this card or Discard this card:</span> Summon 1 independent Proliferated Organism.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3236839158616539816.png",
                "id": "talent37803",
                "key": "Awaken, My Kindred",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_3459993703528451231.png",
                "title": "Awaken, My Kindred"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1941746497727399790.png",
                "id": "talent92634",
                "key": "Proliferated Organism",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_7079169154518254306.png",
                "title": "Proliferated Organism"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_8205911107278783392.png",
                "id": "talent4058",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong><br>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6443406313461739338.png",
